{"title_page": "Subhankar Chattopadhyay", "text_new": "{{Infobox person\n| name          = <!-- use common name/article title -->Subhankar Chattopadhyay\n| image         = <!-- filename only, no \"File:\" or \"Image:\" prefix, and no enclosing [[brackets]] -->\n| alt           = <!-- descriptive text for use by speech synthesis (text-to-speech) software -->\n| caption       = \n| birth_name    = <!-- only use if different from name -->\n| birth_date    = <!-- {{Birth date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}} for living people supply only the year with {{Birth year and age|YYYY}} unless the exact date is already widely published, as per [[WP:DOB]]. For people who have died, use {{Birth date|YYYY|MM|DD}}. -->1977\n| birth_place   = \n| death_date    = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} (DEATH date then BIRTH date) -->\n| death_place   = \n| nationality   = Indian\n| other_names   = \n| occupation    = Film and television director\n| years_active  = \n| known_for     = \n| notable_works = \n}}\n[[File:Subhankar Chattopadhyay.png|alt=Subhankar Chattopadhyay|thumb|Subhankar Chattopadhyay on the set of Bindass Dance]]\n'''Subhankar Chattopadhyay''' ([[Bengali language|Bengali]]:  \u09b6\u09c1\u09ad\u0999\u09cd\u0995\u09b0 \u099a\u099f\u09cd\u099f\u09cb\u09aa\u09be\u09a7\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09af\u09bc; born: 1977) is an Indian  director, script writer , content creator and producer. He is one of the most successful non-fiction show creator in [[Cinema of West Bengal|Tollywood]]. He directed the film [[Handa and Bhonda|Haanda & Bhonda]] (2010) starring [[Mithun Chakraborty]]. He is known for directing famous television shows like [[Dadagiri Unlimited]] , [[Dance Bangla Dance]] ,  [[Mirakkel]] and many more. Subhankar Chattopadhyay and his team has added a unique feather on SCPPL's hat, for being any production house in the history of world television to air their shows twice for a duration of 10 hrs  continuously for Super Singer junior finale and Super Singer audition .  <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ebela.in/entertainment/dadagiri-director-subhankar-chattopadhyay-has-an-other-side-too-dgtl-1.658880|title=\u09b8\u09be\u09ae\u09a8\u09c7 \u098f\u09b2 \u2018\u09a6\u09be\u09a6\u09be\u0997\u09bf\u09b0\u09bf\u2019-\u09aa\u09b0\u09bf\u099a\u09be\u09b2\u0995\u09c7\u09b0 \u0985\u09a8\u09cd\u09af \u09aa\u09b0\u09bf\u099a\u09af\u09bc|last=\u098f\u09ac\u09c7\u09b2\u09be.\u0987\u09a8|first=\u09a8\u09bf\u099c\u09b8\u09cd\u09ac \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a4\u09bf\u09ac\u09c7\u09a6\u09a8|website=ebela.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> <ref>https://bestmediainfo.com/2020/01/star-jalsha-to-host-10-hour-super-audition-for-super-singer/</ref><ref>https://thekolkatamail.com/10-hour-long-super-audition-of-super-singer-to-be-aired-on-12th-january-on-star-jalsha/jalsha-1-4/</ref><ref>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/bengali/super-singer-junior-to-air-its-grand-finale-soon/articleshow/71005558.cms</ref><ref>https://tva.onscreenasia.com/2020/02/star-jalsha-launches-super-singer/\n</ref>\n\n== Life and career ==\nChattopadhyay was born in [[Baruipur]] , [[South 24 Parganas]], [[West Bengal]]. He did his schooling from [[Baruipur High School]] .  He graduated from [[City College, Kolkata|City College]], Kolkata. He started his career at \"[[Literary magazine|Little magazine]]\", forayed into electronic media as a script writer following which he worked for [[Zee Bangla]] as an Executive Producer for many years before directing successful non-fiction shows . He then went on to form a creative team and ventured to start his own company , Subhankar Chattopadhyay Productions Private Limited .<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scppvtltd.com/about-us/|title=About Us \u2013 SCP|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n\n== Works<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scppvtltd.com/our-shows/|title=Our Shows \u2013 SCP|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> ==\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Show\n!Channel\n!Notes\n|-\n|[[Mirakkel]]\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Executive producer|Executive Producer.]] [[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|[[Dance Bangla Dance|Dance Bangla Dance]]\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Executive producer|Executive Producer.]] [[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|[[Dadagiri Unlimited|Dadagiri Unlimited]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/entertainment/dada-s-brat-pack/cid/607358|title=Dada's brat pack|website=www.telegraphindia.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Star of Bengal\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|[[Ke Hobe Biggest Fan|Ke Hobe Biggest Fan]]\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Banglar Shera Poribar\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Apur Sangsar\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Detective 2015\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|Producer\n|-\n|Zee Bangla Gourab Sonman\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Kotha O Kahini<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.grassrootent.com/our-work/|title=OUR WORK \u00ab Grassroot Entertainment Pvt. Ltd|website=www.grassrootent.com|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Bhyabachaka<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.televisionpost.com/star-jalsha-revamps-brand-identity-launches-two-new-weekend-shows/|title=Star Jalsha revamps brand identity, launches two new weekend shows|date=2019-02-21|website=TelevisionPost: Latest News, India\u2019s Television, Cable, DTH,  TRAI|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Amra Na Ora\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Amar Bor Superstar\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|[[Star Jalsha Poribar Awards]]\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Jalsha Doshe Dosh\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Ebar Jombe Moja\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Super Singer Junior\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Dance Dance Junior\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Super Singer<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiantelevision.com/television/tv-channels/regional/star-jalsha-to-host-10-hour-long-super-audition-for-super-singer-200109|title=Star Jalsha to host 10-hour long super audition for Super Singer|date=2020-01-09|website=Indian Television Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.uniindia.com/star-jalsha-launches-super-singer-a-mega-musical-platform-for-youth-of-bengal/east/news/1854411.html|title=UNIINDIA|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Singing Star\n|[[Ruposhi Bangla (TV channel)|Ruposhi Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|-\n|Platinum Pancham<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scppvtltd.com/show/platinum-pancham/|title=Platinum Pancham \u2013 SCP|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|-\n|Bindass Dance\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Abbulish\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|-\n|Rannaghore Rockstar\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|Producer\n|-\n|Gaaner Gunto<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scppvtltd.com/show/gaaner-gnuto/|title=Gaaner Gnuto \u2013 SCP|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|}\n\n=== Filmography<ref>{{Citation|title=Handa And Bhonda Movie Review {3/5}: Critic Review of Handa And Bhonda by Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bengali/movie-reviews/handa-and-bhonda/movie-review/5759434.cms|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Film\n!Year\n!Cast\n!Extra Notes\n|-\n|''[[Handa and Bhonda]]''\n|2010\n|[[Mithun Chakraborty]], [[Aritra Dutta Banik]], [[Biswajit Chakraborty]] and [[Supriya Devi]].\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|}\n\n=== Events ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!EVENT\n!NOTES\n!EXTRA NOTES\n|-\n|[[Mirchi Music Awards Bangla|Mirchi Music Awards bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|\n|-\n|Joyo Hey\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|The entire Bengali film and television fraternity gather for a star-studded evening to celebrate the selfless efforts of the Kolkata Police\n|-\n|100 E Ek Show<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://comingsoon.zee5.com/comingsoon/index.php|title=ZEE5|website=comingsoon.zee5.com|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://comingsoon.zee5.com/comingsoon/index.php|title=ZEE5|website=comingsoon.zee5.com|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|To Celebrate 100 years of Bangla Cinema\n|}\n\n=== Literary Works ===\n<br />\nHe has been practicing his art of writing since years, his writing has also been published in the 'desh' magazine quite a few number of times. In between the year 2000 -2003 his literary pieces 'Tobu j Ami Jiggasha Chinho' and 'Prem Porjoton phaad' was published. Beside this he was also an editor of a magazine called 'Poddyo chorcha'.<ref>https://ebela.in/entertainment/dadagiri-director-subhankar-chattopadhyay-has-an-other-side-too-dgtl-1.658880</ref>\n\n== References ==\n\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox person\n| name          = <!-- use common name/article title -->Subhankar Chattopadhyay\n| image         = <!-- \n<gallery>\nExample.jp\n<gallery>\nExample.jpg|Caption1\nExample.jpg|Caption2\n</gallery>\ng|Cap\n<gallery>\n\n</gallery>\ntion1\nExample.jpg|Caption2\n</gallery>\nfilename only, no \"File:\" or \"Image:\" prefix, and no enclosing [[brackets]] -->\n| alt           = <!-- descriptive text for use by speech synthesis (text-to-speech) software -->\n| caption       = \n| birth_name    = <!-- only use if different from name -->\n| birth_date    = <!-- {{Birth date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}} for living people supply only the year with {{Birth year and age|YYYY}} unless the exact date is already widely published, as per [[WP:DOB]]. For people who have died, use {{Birth date|YYYY|MM|DD}}. -->1977\n| birth_place   = \n| death_date    = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} (DEATH date then BIRTH date) -->\n| death_place   = \n| nationality   = Indian\n| other_names   = \n| occupation    = Film and television director\n| years_active  = \n| known_for     = \n| notable_works = \n}}\n[[File:Subhankar Chattopadhyay.png|alt=Subhankar Chattopadhyay|thumb|Subhankar Chattopadhyay on the set of Bindass Dance]]\n'''Subhankar Chattopadhyay''' ([[Bengali language|Bengali]]:  \u09b6\u09c1\u09ad\u0999\u09cd\u0995\u09b0 \u099a\u099f\u09cd\u099f\u09cb\u09aa\u09be\u09a7\u09cd\u09af\u09be\u09af\u09bc; born: 1977) is an Indian  director, script writer , content creator and producer. He is one of the most successful non-fiction show creator in [[Cinema of West Bengal|Tollywood]]. He directed the film [[Handa and Bhonda|Haanda & Bhonda]] (2010) starring [[Mithun Chakraborty]]. He is known for directing famous television shows like [[Dadagiri Unlimited]] , [[Dance Bangla Dance]] ,  [[Mirakkel]] and many more. Subhankar Chattopadhyay and his team has added a unique feather on SCPPL's hat, for being any production house in the history of world television to air their shows twice for a duration of 10 hrs  continuously for Super Singer junior finale and Super Singer audition .  <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ebela.in/entertainment/dadagiri-director-subhankar-chattopadhyay-has-an-other-side-too-dgtl-1.658880|title=\u09b8\u09be\u09ae\u09a8\u09c7 \u098f\u09b2 \u2018\u09a6\u09be\u09a6\u09be\u0997\u09bf\u09b0\u09bf\u2019-\u09aa\u09b0\u09bf\u099a\u09be\u09b2\u0995\u09c7\u09b0 \u0985\u09a8\u09cd\u09af \u09aa\u09b0\u09bf\u099a\u09af\u09bc|last=\u098f\u09ac\u09c7\u09b2\u09be.\u0987\u09a8|first=\u09a8\u09bf\u099c\u09b8\u09cd\u09ac \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a4\u09bf\u09ac\u09c7\u09a6\u09a8|website=ebela.in|language=en|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> <ref>https://bestmediainfo.com/2020/01/star-jalsha-to-host-10-hour-super-audition-for-super-singer/</ref><ref>https://thekolkatamail.com/10-hour-long-super-audition-of-super-singer-to-be-aired-on-12th-january-on-star-jalsha/jalsha-1-4/</ref><ref>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/bengali/super-singer-junior-to-air-its-grand-finale-soon/articleshow/71005558.cms</ref><ref>https://tva.onscreenasia.com/2020/02/star-jalsha-launches-super-singer/\n<gallery>\nExample.jpg|Caption1\nExample.jpg|Caption2\n</gallery>\n</ref>\n\n== Life and career ==\nChattopadhyay was born in [[Baruipur]] , [[South 24 Parganas]], [[West Bengal]]. He did his schooling from [[Baruipur High School]] .  He graduated from [[City College, Kolkata|City College]], Kolkata. He started his career at \"[[Literary magazine|Little magazine]]\", forayed into electronic media as a script writer following which he worked for [[Zee Bangla]] as an Executive Producer for many years before directing successful non-fiction shows . He then went on to form a creative team and ventured to start his own company , Subhankar Chattopadhyay Productions Private Limited .<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scppvtltd.com/about-us/|title=About Us \u2013 SCP|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n\n== Works<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scppvtltd.com/our-shows/|title=Our Shows \u2013 SCP|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> ==\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Show\n!Channel\n!Notes\n|-\n|[[Mirakkel]]\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Executive producer|Executive Producer.]] [[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|[[Dance Bangla Dance|Dance Bangla Dance]]\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Executive producer|Executive Producer.]] [[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|[[Dadagiri Unlimited|Dadagiri Unlimited]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.telegraphindia.com/entertainment/dada-s-brat-pack/cid/607358|title=Dada's brat pack|website=www.telegraphindia.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Star of Bengal\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|[[Ke Hobe Biggest Fan|Ke Hobe Biggest Fan]]\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Banglar Shera Poribar\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Apur Sangsar\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Detective 2015\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|Producer\n|-\n|Zee Bangla Gourab Sonman\n|[[Zee Bangla|Zee bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Kotha O Kahini<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.grassrootent.com/our-work/|title=OUR WORK \u00ab Grassroot Entertainment Pvt. Ltd|website=www.grassrootent.com|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Bhyabachaka<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.televisionpost.com/star-jalsha-revamps-brand-identity-launches-two-new-weekend-shows/|title=Star Jalsha revamps brand identity, launches two new weekend shows|date=2019-02-21|website=TelevisionPost: Latest News, India\u2019s Television, Cable, DTH,  TRAI|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Amra Na Ora\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Amar Bor Superstar\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|[[Star Jalsha Poribar Awards]]\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]]\n|-\n|Jalsha Doshe Dosh\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Ebar Jombe Moja\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Super Singer Junior\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Dance Dance Junior\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Super Singer<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiantelevision.com/television/tv-channels/regional/star-jalsha-to-host-10-hour-long-super-audition-for-super-singer-200109|title=Star Jalsha to host 10-hour long super audition for Super Singer|date=2020-01-09|website=Indian Television Dot Com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.uniindia.com/star-jalsha-launches-super-singer-a-mega-musical-platform-for-youth-of-bengal/east/news/1854411.html|title=UNIINDIA|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|[[Star Jalsha]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Singing Star\n|[[Ruposhi Bangla (TV channel)|Ruposhi Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|-\n|Platinum Pancham<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scppvtltd.com/show/platinum-pancham/|title=Platinum Pancham \u2013 SCP|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|-\n|Bindass Dance\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|-\n|Abbulish\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|-\n|Rannaghore Rockstar\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|Producer\n|-\n|Gaaner Gunto<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://scppvtltd.com/show/gaaner-gnuto/|title=Gaaner Gnuto \u2013 SCP|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref>\n|[[Colors Bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] , Producer\n|}\n\n=== Filmography<ref>{{Citation|title=Handa And Bhonda Movie Review {3/5}: Critic Review of Handa And Bhonda by Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bengali/movie-reviews/handa-and-bhonda/movie-review/5759434.cms|access-date=2020-04-02}}</ref> ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Film\n!Year\n!Cast\n!Extra Notes\n|-\n|''[[Handa and Bhonda]]''\n|2010\n|[[Mithun Chakraborty]], [[Aritra Dutta Banik]], [[Biswajit Chakraborty]] and [[Supriya Devi]].\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|}\n\n=== Events ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!EVENT\n!NOTES\n!EXTRA NOTES\n|-\n|[[Mirchi Music Awards Bangla|Mirchi Music Awards bangla]]\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|\n|-\n|Joyo Hey\n|[[Film director|Director]] \n|The entire Bengali film and television fraternity gather for a star-studded evening to celebrate t